entries.title_d: A cloak representative wishes to speak with you personally, possibly about working as a double-agent. CorSec command thinks that this may be a prime opportunity to go undercover, however, this could be a potentially dangerous assignment. You are to travel to the pre-arranged meeting location. Dock with the representative if you wish to go undercover, otherwise just blow him to space dust.
entries.title: Corellia System: Meet the Cloak Representative
entries.split_quest_alert_fail: Cloak Representative destroyed. Acceptable within mission parameters.
entries.split_quest_alert: Incoming mission. Acquire CorSec Transport security codes and deliver them to the Cloak Representative.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the navigation waypoint and meet the Cloak Representative.
entries.quest_location_d: The meeting location is set up in the Corellia system.
entries.quest_dock2_t: Dock With or Destroy the Cloak Representative
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the Cloak representative if you wish to go undercover and work with the Cloaks, otherwise just destroy him.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, CorSec. I'm glad you decided to come. Dock with my ship if you're interested in what I have to say.
entries.found_loc_d: You should have the coordinates for the meeting location. Go ahead and dock with the Cloak rep if you're comfortable with going undercover, otherwise just destroy him.
entries.failed_destroyed: We copy, pilot. Confirming destruction of the Cloak Representative. No love lost, here. Go ahead and come back to the station for debriefing.
entries.docking_started_delivery: You've made the right choice, CorSec. Now let me tell you about the Cloaks. I think you'll find it interesting.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: I'm glad to hear that you've decided to work with us. Of course, you musn't tell CorSec Command. Now for a small test of your commitment.
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: <\#pcontrast3  Warning. Enemy craft inbound.\#pcontrast1 >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Roger that. Looks like you're at the right spot. The Cloak representative should be arriving shortly. Stand by.
